{"tid":1742884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣布終止黎明行動，下一步就係要終止埋假日抗爭","createTime":"2019-11-21T03:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T11:34:01.000Z","uid":240250,"like":7,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f49cc25381ba445ea72570cd9945e9af2930ec10","tid":1742884,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:31:26.000Z","msg":"黎明行動成果有目共睹，不旦對政府零影響，反而令一眾打工仔怨聲載道，民意盡失，好多人都喺呢兩個星期由黃轉藍。<br />\n另外，經過理大一役，眾多前線手足被捕，勇武路線壽終正寢，加上警方頻頻唔批不反，令和理非卻步，假日抗爭已經唔會再有威力。<br />\n<br />\n明刀明槍嘅抗爭運動已經唔可行，我哋需要轉形為地下運動。<br />\n實際建議：<br />\n1. 每日準時返工返學（最重要，留有用之軀好好裝備自己）<br />\n2. 唔好再沉迷街頭抗爭，集中網絡宣傳、國際戰線<br />\n3. 務求做到對現實生活零影響，做左都冇人知<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa03562ec3816533b83c1c1f0fec4c7c1b684f86","tid":1742884,"uid":205162,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:32:23.000Z","msg":"徐永強  完全封鎖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db120653c54a4d084cb23994fa37ca7ba9d8f1c8","tid":1742884,"uid":32051,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:33:01.000Z","msg":"怕影響民意<br />\n我決定乜都唔做了"},{"pid":"f3bcc4f7c1d524d205cf55b6420dd5b2ae2051b4","tid":1742884,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:33:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5089d73bd39ed362f5633301ceeefc9dd6839e6c","tid":1742884,"uid":146520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:36:22.000Z","msg":"黃轉藍都講得出<br />\n我話你條賓周變咗閪窿都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8101d6e6d2df9466e94f99359f958f72bbc9cd","tid":1742884,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa03562ec3816533b83c1c1f0fec4c7c1b684f86","tid":1742884,"uid":205162,"like":8,